The paper discusses the challenges of human-robot teaming, which is a subfield of robotics (cs.RO) that involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The paper also mentions the need for changes to the traditional view of autonomous agents, which could fall under the category of systems and control (cs.SY) or machine learning (cs.MA).
